916
00:41:18,600 --> 00:41:20,280
If she tries to reach high,

917
00:41:21,160 --> 00:41:21,880
I will be

918
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:23,240
coughing up blood.

919
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:26,640
Mother, just treat it

920
00:41:26,640 --> 00:41:27,680
as planning

921
00:41:27,680 --> 00:41:28,480
the future of Young Sixth Miss

922
00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:30,440
Grandmother had Sixth Miss

923
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:32,880
look at his son.

924
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:34,680
If Sixth Sister

925
00:41:34,680 --> 00:41:35,600
can find a good husband,

926
00:41:35,760 --> 00:41:37,240
Grandmother will be very happy too.

927
00:41:38,160 --> 00:41:39,600
Since I've had my daughter,

928
00:41:39,600 --> 00:41:40,720
