929
00:41:41,160 --> 00:41:42,320
Grandmother put aside her pride

930
00:41:42,320 --> 00:41:44,000
and found Old Madam He,

931
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:45,320
and plotted for us

932
00:41:45,640 --> 00:41:46,560
to have Sixth Miss

933
00:41:46,560 --> 00:41:47,600
come out and manage house.

934
00:41:47,880 --> 00:41:49,080
So the house key

935
00:41:49,080 --> 00:41:49,760
was spared

936
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:50,800
from falling into that Mistress Lin's hands.

937
00:41:52,280 --> 00:41:52,837
This is all due to

938
